OL,3,CBarriers to stalking orders reduced to
OL,4,Cimprove protection access
OL,6,FReforms will be introduced to make it
OL,7,Feasier to obtain stalking protection
OL,8,Forder, to better protect victims of
OL,9,Fthe crime
OL,11,FPolice officers will face fewer
OL,12,Fbarriers to obtaining court orders to
OL,13,Fprotect victims of stalking, under
OL,14,Fchanges announced on Monday.
OL,16,FUpdated Home Office guidance means
OL,17,Fofficers will no longer have to meet
OL,18,Fthe criminal standard of evidence when
OL,19,Fapplying for stalking protection
OL,20,Forders (SPOs), and will instead have
OL,21,Fto meet the lower civil standard.
