OL,6,FVictims minister Laura Farris said the
OL,7,Fchanges would make "a big difference
OL,8,Fto how easily victims can access
OL,9,Fprotection".
OL,11,FShe said: "Stalking is a complex form
OL,12,Fof abuse, and it can have a
OL,13,Fdevastating impact on the lives of
OL,14,Fvictims and their families. Sadly, it
OL,15,Fcan end in the most tragic
OL,16,Fcircumstances.
