OL,3,CBarriers to stalking orders reduced to
OL,4,Cimprove protection access
OL,6,F"We must continue to treat stalking
OL,7,Fwith the utmost gravity. Having
OL,8,Fdoubled the maximum sentence and
OL,9,Fintroduced a new civil order to
OL,10,Fprotect victims, we know there is more
OL,11,Fwe must do."
OL,13,FIn 2017, the government increased the
OL,14,Fmaximum sentence for the most serious
OL,15,Fkinds of stalking from five years to
OL,16,F10 years.
