OL,6,FMonday's guidance states it is
OL,7,F"likely" that courts will accept the
OL,8,Flower civil standard of proof when
OL,9,Fdeciding to grant SPOs, relying on the
OL,10,Fbalance of probabilities rather than
OL,11,Fthe criminal standard of "beyond
OL,12,Freasonable doubt".
OL,14,FThat assessment is based on a case
OL,15,Fabout anti-social behaviour orders
OL,16,Ffrom 2003.
