OL,6,FEmma Lingley-Clark, chief executive of
OL,7,Fcharity the Suzy Lamplugh Trust,
OL,8,Fwelcomed the changes, saying the
OL,9,Fprevious standard had been "a barrier
OL,10,Fto victims getting immediate
OL,11,Fprotection when they need it the most".
OL,13,FMs Lingley-Clark also called for an
OL,14,Fincrease in the use of SPOs across the
OL,15,Fcountry and said police officers'
OL,16,Funderstanding of the orders needed to
OL,17,Fbe improved.
